Class ServiceObjectiveOperationsImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.microsoft.windowsazure.management.sql.ServiceObjectiveOperationsImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ServiceOperations<SqlManagementClientImpl>, ServiceObjectiveOperations

    public class ServiceObjectiveOperationsImpl
extends java.lang.Object
implements ServiceOperations<SqlManagementClientImpl>, ServiceObjectiveOperations
    This class provides methods to get a specific service objective by using its ID or to List all of the service objectives on a server.
